A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Hunter Safety Education – Issuance of Identification Number
3 FOR the purpose of requiring the Department of Natural Resources to issue a permanent
4 identification number in a certain manner to each person who successfully completes
5 a course of instruction in conservation and in competency and safety in the handling
6 of firearms; and generally relating to hunter safety education.
